# Search Engine Skill

A specialized skill for searching drone-related professional activities using multiple search methods.

## Description
This skill orchestrates the search process using both SearxNG for broad searches and WebFetch for targeted scraping from professional sites.

## Configuration
- search_timeout: 600 seconds
- max_results_per_source: 20
- deduplication: enabled
- result_storage: enabled

## Functions
- universal_search: Performs broad search using SearxNG across multiple engines
- targeted_fetch: Performs targeted scraping from professional sites
- store_results: Stores search results in designated databases
- get_search_stats: Returns statistics about recent searches